      "text": "A 28-year-old man is brought to the emergency department with a gunshot wound to the chest. The patient's friend who is a ballistic expert by profession claims to have witnessed the shooting. During the investigation, the police also consult another ballistics expert. In court, which of the following statements about the types of witnesses involved is most accurate?",
