          "text": "Both the patient's friend and the ballistics expert are considered expert witnesses",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "The patient's friend is a common witness as well as expert witness, while the ballistics expert is an expert witness",
          "correct": true
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "The patient's friend is a common witness only, while the ballistics expert is an expert witness",
          "correct": false
