      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:637px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Section of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"270c00aff316927771839a8749b963\">BSA</span> (Bhartiya Sakshya Act) </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Explanation/Provision</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>143 BSA</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>The sequence of examination (Oath-CH-CR-RE)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>146 (1) (2) (3) <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"270c00aff316927771839a8749b963\">BSA</span> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Leading question</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>157 BSA</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Questions by the party to his/her own witness</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>168 BSA</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>A magistrate or judge can ask you a question at any point of time</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\u00a0\n\t\t\t<p><strong>124 BSA</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\u00a0\n\t\t\t<p>A competent witness is one who has the capacity and ability to understand the questions put to him by the court. If he has the understanding of questions and the ability to give rational answers, then he is a competent witness.</p>\n<p><strong>(Common Witness)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>39 BSA</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #808080; border-left:1px solid #808080; border-right:1px solid #808080; border-top:1px solid #808080; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>A person especially skilled in foreign law, science</p>\n<p>or art is an<strong> Expert witness</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
